<!-- Purpose:To test the SELECT element with the SIZE attribute.-->

<!-- Expected result: A list box should be displayed with all six items visible -->

<title>XHTML Functional -- SELECT - SIZE</title>

</head>

<body>

The list box displayed below is created with a SELECT element. The

list box contains six items which should all be visible without

scrolling. This effect is set by the SIZE attribute. 



<form><select name="flavor" size="6">

<option>Vanilla</option>

<option>Chocolate</option>

<option>Strawberry</option>

<option>Kiwi</option>

<option>Coffee</option>

<option>Peanut Butter</option>

</select></form>

</body>

